    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 1 },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "content": "## Sparc Energy — Local Dev Stack\n\n**API:** [localhost:8000/health](http://localhost:8000/health)  \n**Docs:** [localhost:8000/docs](http://localhost:8000/docs)  \n**Stack:** FastAPI · TimescaleDB · Redis · LightGBM  \n\n> Rows will populate once ESB CSV is uploaded and demo is run.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "",
